{"type":null,"faqId":49400,"title":"编辑文本","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4763889in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"编辑文字\"XE \"选取文字\"XE \"选择文字\"XE \"复制文字\"XE \"剪切文字\"XE \"粘贴文本\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"编辑文本\"您可以对文本进行选取、剪切、复制和粘贴等操作。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188990\" style=\"width:3.129861in;height:1.6666666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n <span>XE \"选取文本\"</span><span class=\"s2\">选取文本</span><span>：长按文字区域，直至出现“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188991\" style=\"width:0.18055555in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，拖动“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188995\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”和“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188996\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”选择要编辑的文本，或点击“全选”选择全部文字。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>XE \"复制文本\"</span><span class=\"s2\">复制文本</span><span>：选取文本后，点击“复制”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>XE \"剪切文本\"</span><span class=\"s2\">剪切文本</span><span>：选取文本后，点击“剪切”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>XE \"粘贴文本\"</span><span class=\"s2\">粘贴文本</span><span>：长按选择文本插入点，点击“粘贴”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188997\" style=\"width:3.2305555in;height:1.6666666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<br>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1090,"faqType":"开始使用","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5144","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Getting-know-phone","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447294340000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":30,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}